  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de hdwids</title>

    <para>
      Installez <application>hdwids</application> en lançant les commandes suivantes :
      commands, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>for ids in pci.ids usb.ids; do
  install -vDm644 $ids usr/share/hwdata/$ids
done &amp;&amp;
unset ids</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>
